name: Commons and Cove
description:
This week we will make our way to the Dartmouth Common for a loop around the baseball field and then head to the Dartmouth Cove trail. Once there we will run along the waterfront until Old Ferry Rd and then return to the Gazebo via Newcastle., Albert, and Hawthorne Streets
As always, we meet at the Sullivans Pond Gazebo at 6:30pm.
